data.name: label1.Text
data.value: To create an invoice, select a date range, filter by shipper/bill-to as needed, and add bills to the invoice contents. When ready, click the button to create the new invoice. Note well: all bills on an invoice must have the same shipper and bill-to clients and must have dates.

data.name: label15.Text
data.value: To review invoices, select a date range, filter by shipper/bill-to as needed, and use the controls to take whatever steps are necessary. Note well: once an invoice has been finalized, its RFS calculations will cease and the invoice will be locked.
